node.text: I receive hundreds of messages daily from people asking me for advice so i decided to partner with @CAMEO @cameoespanol and will be accepting bookings starting Saturday on cameo.com or through their official app. You can request shoutouts, wish someone a happy birthday, a life changing motivational message, review your track/podcast/tv show/film/music video and give my honest opinion, promote your upcoming release or even ask me things such as how to invest less than $100USD and make hundreds or thousands of dollars within minutes.
